{"tid":251012,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦瘋狂重新開機","createTime":"2017-05-20T14:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T14:51:35.000Z","uid":29595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf75ec2e468af11a23e6acfcea7ca19a0002495","tid":251012,"uid":29595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"部電腦好似中左唔知咩毒 load唔到window<br />\n<br />\n 不斷重新開機無限loop<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知道點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d85e47499ffecb8219995bcf2aa2989be73843","tid":251012,"uid":84057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"先試用safe mode入 備份重資料 試修復windows<br />\n唔得用no name入備份data<br />\n重裝windows<br />\n放棄搵中咩毒啦"},{"pid":"1d7ce3a2ab9d8c2959100d68d38b82cc6bc4850b","tid":251012,"uid":84057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"假設你真係windows corrupt 左先咁做<br />\n<br />\n不停重開可以有其他原因<br />\n中毒你都係斷估姐"},{"pid":"e4356676e14fcdada8133be1b02ef86f83d58f55","tid":251012,"uid":29595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設你真係windows corrupt 左先咁做<br />\n<br />\n不停重開可以有其他原因<br />\n中毒你都係斷估姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用window個重設都唔得 話咩發生意外的錯誤，Windows無法進行安裝。咁係咪要搵返隻window碟重裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387cf800fd74f292364d94abbdf002d670ab5e33","tid":251012,"uid":29595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:51:35.000Z","msg":"卡左係window10 loading既畫面 <br />\n<br />\n不停轉圈 之後就彈 <br />\n<br />\n電腦意外地重新啟動或發生意外的錯誤。Windows無法進<br />\n<br />\n行安裝。若要安裝Windows，請按一下確定重新啟動電腦<br />\n<br />\n，然後重新啟動安裝程式。<br />\n<br />\n當我按左確定之後，就會開始瘋狂重新開機不停loop<br />\n<br />\n之後又彈出嚟又叫你按確定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}